      "settings": {
        "heading": "A Journey That Began with One Man’s Dream and Grew Through the Trust of the People",
        "subheading": "Behind every success story lies a struggle.",
        "description": "<p>The journey of <strong>K. Chinnadurai Gold House & Textiles</strong> is a true story that began with the dream of an ordinary man and blossomed into a trusted brand.</p><p>Mr. <strong>K. Chinnadurai</strong> gained valuable business experience during his youth while working in a textile store. Through daily interactions with customers and by learning the intricacies of retail business, a dream began to take shape in his mind:</p><p><em>“One day, we too should establish our own store and provide quality products to people.”</em></p><p>What started as a small dream gradually became the foundation of a successful enterprise that now operates across multiple cities.</p>",
        "padding_top": 60,
        "padding_bottom": 60
      }
    },
